response.original_title: Vulcan Gas Company: A Cultural Utility
response.overview: Deep history of the original Vulcan Gas Company music venue and its run from 1968 through 1970. It covers their ground breaking light shows, the invention of their sound system, and the historic performances by Johny Winter, Steve Miller, and Stevie Ray Vaughn.
response.tagline: A Cultural Utility, by Barry Underhill
response.title: Vulcan Gas Company: A Cultural Utility
